  "title": "supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will lead and oversee a team of case managers in a TCM clinic, ensuring effective support for individuals with complex needs through strategic supervision and operational management.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and coordinate a team of case managers to deliver comprehensive care for individuals with complex needs</li><li>Develop and implement strategies to optimize case management processes and improve patient outcomes</li><li>Monitor team performance and provide coaching to enhance skills and service quality</li><li>Collaborate with healthcare professionals to ensure integrated and patient-centered care delivery</li><li>Manage clinic operations to maintain compliance with healthcare standards and regulations</li><li>Analyze case data to identify trends and inform continuous improvement initiatives</li></ul>",
